# Applies to the repo-root build context used by Backend/*/Dockerfile

**/bin/
**/obj/
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/*.user

# Frontend has its own build context/.dockerignore; exclude it here too
# so backend image builds never pull in node_modules by accident.
Frontend/ScriptFlow-UI/node_modules/
Frontend/ScriptFlow-UI/dist/
Frontend/ScriptFlow-UI/.angular/

.git/
.github/
*.md
SPEC/
Prompts/
Skills/
